;; TEST-PURPOSE: A known function call accepts a parenthesized infix expression as a later argument.
;; TEST-ATOM: gcd2 b (a mod b) parses as (gcd2 b (mod a b)), not as an infix rewrite around b.
;; TEST-EXPECT: compile, run
;; TEST-COVERAGE: reader function-call versus infix promotion slot handling
;; TEST-USES-ATOM: atom.codegen.functions.known.call.parenthesized.infix.arg
;; TEST-MENU: branches/functions/known-call-parenthesized-infix-arg/atom.codegen.functions.known.call.parenthesized.infix.arg
